Public Service Announcement: The Importance of Lighting (Or, "I almost left the house like this")
data.description:
The first picture was taken in a bathroom with regular incandescent dressing room bulbs. I thought everything looked okay.

The second picture was taken about 5 minutes later in the car with natural light.  Note: I did NOT CHANGE or add/remove/blend any makeup between the two pictures! Check out the foundation unibrow, unblended hairline, garishly horrifying clownish blush, and much brighter pink lips. Always, always, always check your makeup in different lighting!
